{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23152.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day17.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"[surround:8048_hospitaldoor]*Rattle...*","narrationBg":"bg_adv_23152.jpg","narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"narrationEffect":"out"},{"chara":[{"id":200401}],"nameAvCenter":"Sayaka","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]How are you feeling, Kyosuke?","textAvColor":"textSayaka"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":200401,"pos":2}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":810501,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyosuke","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Sayaka..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Huh? What's wrong?"},{"bgm":"bgm02_anime03","chara":[{"id":810501,"motion":300}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyosuke","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]About yesterday... I'm sorry for@what I said! I'm really sorry!"},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":400}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20][chara:200401:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Hey, hold on a second!@What's the matter?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":810501},{"id":200401,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyosuke","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Yesterday, I did something@I'm really ashamed of."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":810501}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyosuke","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]After finding out my injury was worse@than I thought, I lashed out at you..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":810501,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyosuke","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Like that was gonna help anything..."},{"chara":[{"id":810501,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyosuke","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You never stopped caring about me@this whole time..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":810501,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyosuke","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You still came today, even after@I said such terrible things..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Um...@Did you say something to me?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":200401,"pos":2},{"eyeClose":0,"id":810501}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Haha.@To be honest, I don't really remember."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":1}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But you're the kind of guy who reflects@on things and fixes your flaws..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Instead of running away from your@weaknesses, you face them head on."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200401,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I like that side of you, Kyosuke."},{"chara":[{"id":810501,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyosuke","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Sayaka..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Miracles and magic...@Sure, those would make things easier."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]But even without them,@you can stand on your own two feet."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":201}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]That's just who you are,@Kyosuke Kamijo. No?"},{"chara":[{"id":810501,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyosuke","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I...don't know if I can do this."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Hmm, well..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Then I'll stay by your side to support you!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":100}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]...Maybe?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810501},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyosuke","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Thanks, Sayaka."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":810501,"motion":100},{"id":200401,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Kyosuke","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It's good to know I can count on you."},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Sure thing."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
